text:
What parent wouldn't suffer for their child? If you knew that you could sacrifice yourself to save not just your own children, but countless others, wouldn't you? Surely it is better for one person to go to hell than it is for that many more to have the chance to fall.

&#x200B;

In fact, isn't that similar to what Jesus is supposed to have done? He endured a great amount of suffering specifically to save other people.  What makes this decision any less good?
